OL,3,CMatthew Perry was 'lonely in his soul'
OL,4,Csays family on death anniversary
OL,6,FMatthew Perry's family has said he was
OL,7,F"very lonely" during an interview
OL,8,Fmarking the first anniversary of his
OL,9,Fdeath.
OL,11,FThe Friends actor was found dead in a
OL,12,Fhot tub at his home in Los Angeles on
OL,13,FOctober 28, 2023, with a lethal amount
OL,14,Fof ketamine in his bloodstream.
OL,16,FIn an exclusive interview with NBC's
OL,17,FToday, Perry's mother Suzanne Morrison
OL,18,Fsaid that despite his personality
OL,19,F"lighting up the room", he was "very
OL,20,Flonely in his soul".
