OL,3,CMatthew Perry was 'lonely in his soul'
OL,4,Csays family on death anniversary
OL,6,FShe also spoke of an apparent
OL,7,F"premonition" which Perry seemed to
OL,8,Fhave ahead of his own death.
OL,10,F"There was an inevitability to what
OL,11,Fwas going to happen to him next, and
OL,12,Fhe felt it very strongly," she told
OL,13,FNBC. "But he said 'I'm not frightened
OL,14,Fany more', and it worried me."
OL,16,FPerry struggled with addiction for
OL,17,Fyears, even during his time on the hit
OL,18,F90s sitcom Friends, where he played
OL,19,FChandler Bing alongside Jennifer
OL,20,FAniston, Courteney Cox, Lisa Kudrow,
OL,21,FMatt LeBlanc, and David Schwimmer.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
