OL,4,Csays family on death anniversary
OL,6,FPerry's stepfather and sisters also
OL,7,Fpaid tribute to the star, speaking of
OL,8,Fhis experiences with addiction.
OL,10,F"Even when he was struggling in dark
OL,11,Ftimes, we were always proud of him,"
OL,12,FCaitlin Morrison, Perry's sister, said.
OL,14,F"We were always proud of the fact he
OL,15,Fkept fighting. He made it a focus of
OL,16,Fhis life to help other people."
