OL,3,CMatthew Perry was 'lonely in his soul'
OL,4,Csays family on death anniversary
OL,6,FKeith Morrison, Perry's stepfather,
OL,7,Fadded: "People come up to us all the
OL,8,Ftime and say sorry for your loss.
OL,9,FMillions of people have had that loss.
OL,10,FWe're very aware of that. This is not
OL,11,Fabout us, it's about those millions of
OL,12,Fpeople."
OL,14,FHis family also spoke of the comfort
OL,15,Fthey felt in seeing criminal
OL,16,Fproceedings take place into the
OL,17,Fcircumstances of his death.
